Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:37.93,中文对白,,0,0,0,,good morning everyone have a nice day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:40.34,日文对白,,0,0,0,,ドキドキ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:40.34,中文对白,,0,0,0,,紧张紧张……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.72,日文对白,,0,0,0,,have a nice day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.72,中文对白,,0,0,0,,have a nice day
